  "body": "I helped a user troubleshoot an issue with EBS volumes not being formatted correctly today and found that there is almost no logging to help determine what happened when mkfs or mount fails.  In my particular case, it's not even clear whether `mkfs` was ever run.  So, we should:\n1.  Ensure that the shared `SafeFormatAndMount` code has appropriate logging\n2.  Ensure that the EBS volume code has appropriate logging\n",
